invented, semi-wet process, which combines the benefits of precipitation and fusion. The production process is energy-saving and pollution-free, with high product purity, low free acid value, and excellent lubricity. Hailed as one of the best&nbsp;<strong>calcium Stearate exporters in the World</strong>, we assure you that you will never be disappointed with our products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>What is the Standard for Choosing Calcium Stearate?</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The calcium stearate standard is based on different industries. Generally, we mainly choose calcium stearate based on the application field and our own experience. Generally a good stearate should have white colour, free from contamination, low free fatty acid, low electrolyte contents, low free alkali, high thermal stability and negligible heavy metal contents. For more information, you can contact us, and we will definitely guide you in your selection based on your needs and requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Why Mla Calcium Stearate is Good for Plastics ?</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have a full fledged in-house plastic lab equipped with a two roll mill, moulding press, rheometer, pilot extruder, VR tester, congo red tester, stability ovens etc. to develop high performance products that give excellent gelation and internal lubrication. We have in house Pipe and cable technologists to provide technical support to our customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '<h2>Applications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the&nbsp;<strong>leading Calcium Stearate supplier in India</strong>, we supply a product that is of excellent performance and reliable quality that is widely used in food, medicine, cosmetics, plastic, and rubber industries, mainly as lubricants, emulsifiers, stabilizers, mold release agents, accelerators, cosmetic base materials, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is mainly used for application in the following areas:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>As a waterproofing agent, lubricant, and plastic auxiliary.</li>\r\n	<li>It can also be used for non-toxic soft films such as food packaging and medical appliances.</li>\r\n	<li>As a heat stabilizer for polyvinyl chloride, a lubricant for a variety of plastic processing, and a mold release agent.</li>\r\n	<li>As a halogen absorbent in polyethylene and polypropylene, it can eliminate the adverse effects of residual catalyst in the resin on the color and stability of the resin.</li>\r\n	<li>As a plasticizer in rubber processing, it can soften natural rubber and synthetic rubber, but has almost no effect on vulcanization.</li>\r\n	<li>In the production of pencil lead, medicine, cosmetics and perfume industry.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2024-04-25 07:58:33', '2024-12-04 07:49:05'),
