n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Leading Magnesium Stearate manufacturer & supplier in India\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Buy Magnesium Stearate from the best manufacturers in India, we are the leading supplier & exporter of Stearate in the world, offering quality at affordability\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/magenisium-sterate.webp\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/magnesium-stearate-manufacturers.html\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:logo\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/images/logo-MLA.png\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/magnesium-stearate-manufacturers.html\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Leading Magnesium Stearate manufacturer & supplier in India\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/magenisium-sterate.webp\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Buy Magnesium Stearate from the best manufacturers in India, we are the leading supplier & exporter of Stearate in the world, offering quality at affordability\" />\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:creator\" content=\"MLA Group\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'product-image/magenisium-sterate_1.webp', NULL, '17', 'Unpublished', '<h2>Magnesium Stearate Exporter in India</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group of Industries is a prominent name among Magnesium Stearate manufacturers in India. Operating for over 45 years in the production, supply, and export of chemicals, we hold immense industry experience in manufacturing all kinds of metallic stearates including Magnesium Stearate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a massive production capacity of 800 tons per month, we are today a Leading Magnesium Stearate supplier not only in India but also in the world. Our company has strong production technology, advanced scientific research, and a perfect quality management system, and its products have been sold to all provinces and cities across the country and worldwide. It is because of our diligent customer service and fair market prices that our company occupies one of the leading positions among competitors in the sales of magnesium stearate. We export to 45 countries and are a STAR EXPORT HOUSE certified by the Indian government.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We specialize in the production of&nbsp;<strong>pharma grade Magnesium Stearate&nbsp;</strong>with materials conforming to IP / BP/ USP / EP / JP / NF.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Product - Magnesium Stearate</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Magnesium Stearate is a magnesium salt of stearic acid. It is an additive widely used by the pharmacological area because it provides various functionalities to the formulations since it has lubricating, water-repellent, anti-flake, and release properties which attribute it to the products that are made with it. It is also used in plastics as a lubricant.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Magnesium Stearate Properties</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>It is a light white powder with a fine appearance.</li>\r\n	<li>It feels smooth and greasy.</li>\r\n	<li>It is insoluble in water, ethanol, and ether.</li>\r\n	<li>It is soluble in hot water and hot ethanol.</li>\r\n	<li>It decomposes into stearic acid and the corresponding magnesium salt when acidic.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why Choose Us as Your Magnesium Stearate Suppliers In India ?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We are favored by customers for our excellent product quality, good company reputation, and perfect after-sales service. We have developed rapidly under the guidance of the rigorous, pragmatic, efficient, and lean development concept introduced advanced technology and equipment, and have a complete set of equipment production lines, which has laid a solid foundation for the company&#39;s sustainable development. We work with a group of diligent professionals, who are well-trained and experienced in the realm of producing superior quality Magnesium Stearate. With the production and management philosophy of &quot;customize and specialize&quot; and &quot;beginning with customer needs and ending with customer satisfaction&quot;, our company has won praise from users and has become one of the leading magnesium stearate suppliers in the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Approach</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>At MLA Group, we always adhere to the business philosophy of &ldquo;quality first, integrity first,&rdquo; through continuous innovation and progress. We are constantly applying new technologies and new processes, actively developing new products, reducing costs, and improving quality. It is the purpose of our company to provide all customers with timely, complete, and high-quality sales services.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Certifications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our manufacturing facility is</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>ISO 9001: 2015 certified</li>\r\n	<li>GMP Certified</li>\r\n	<li>FDA approved ( FSSAI certified )</li>\r\n	<li>HALAL certified</li>\r\n	<li>Kosher certified</li>\r\n	<li>Drug controller certified ( Pharma Division )</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us now for more information and we will be happy to assist you.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>FAQS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>What is the USP of MLA Magnesium stearate?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA stearates are unique because of not only the stringent process control but also the plant being of totally SS 316 L construction, leading to a very pure product. The product has low free fatty acid, very fine particle size, and is free from contamination as it passed through air classifier as well as mechanical sieving in the final stage of production. There are tailor-made grades as per the application and specifications of the customer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Why should I choose MLA Group as my Magnesium Stearate suppliers?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group of Industries is a leading name engaged in manufacturing and supplying the finest range of Magnesium Stearate. All our products pass through several quality checks at all stages and are deemed fit for dispatch only after thorough consideration of industry laid parameters. We also provide after-sales service and have a strong product recall policy in case of the defective products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How should magnesium stearate be stored?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is recommended to store the magnesium stearate in a dry, ventilated area. You should also avoid direct sunlight and high temperatures. You can store in a closed container; in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area, away from strong oxidizing agents.</p>\r\n', '', '<h2>Applications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We are a leading Magnesium Stearate supplier and exporters of Magnesium Stearate that is widely used in :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Food, medicine, paint, plastics, rubber, textiles, and other industries, mainly as an emulsifier, mold release agent, lubricant, stabilizer, accelerator, cosmetic base material, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>This substance partially replaces the white matt pigment, which also makes it possible to use it in cosmetology. In creams, it acts as a lubricant and significantly increases glide.</li>\r\n	<li>Magnesium stearate is also used as an active stabilizer in PVC production.</li>\r\n	<li>In addition, the substance is used as a supplement in the manufacture of pharmaceuticals.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2024-04-25 08:15:49', '2025-03-17 13:53:34');
