, and coatings. As a&nbsp;<strong>Leading Pharma Excipients suppliers in India</strong>, all our formulations are done in accordance with the set FDA norms and guidelines. Our products are free of all heavy metals, pathogens and impurities, being manufactured in a GMP certified plant following stringent failure, mode, effect analysis.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Advantages:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Pharma Excipients manufacturing is done under very closely controlled conditions, both in terms of infrastructure ( building, machinery, etc ) as well as process ( manpower, records, testing, etc ). The plant in run as per the guidelines in Schedule M.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;We have a stability chamber having adjustable heat and humidity that is used to check the product stability. This provides our customers with data of change in material&#39;s critical properties over a period of 2-3 years if they so require. We also have in house AAS, PSD analyzer, Surface area analyzer.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Pharma raw materials are different from normal because they are going to be used for human consumption. Therefore, to guarantee maximum purity, we have our in-house microbiology lab to make sure that our products are free of all pathogens and heavy metals.</li>\r\n	<li>A company making IP( pharma ) grade products is supposed to ensure that the products it manufactures finally meet the specifications laid down. At MLA Group, we have permission for IP/ BP/USP/EP/JP from the drug controller office or Food and Drug Administration.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Product Range:</h2>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<thead>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>S.No</th>\r\n			<th>Product Name</th>\r\n			<th>Specification</th>\r\n			<th>Use</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>1</td>\r\n			<td>Magnesium Stearate</td>\r\n			<td>IP/BP/USP/EP/JP</td>\r\n			<td>Excipients</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>2</td>\r\n			<td>Calcium Stearate</td>\r\n			<td>IP/BP/USP/EP/JP</td>\r\n			<td>Excipient