ogy, the stability of quality, and the completeness of after-sales service. We never overcharge our customers and there is no concept of opportunity cost in our company. Hence our prices are always most competitive both in domestic and international markets.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Synonyms</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1,2-Bis(stearoylamino) ethane.</li>\r\n	<li>N,N&#39; - Ethylene bis stearamide</li>\r\n	<li>N,N&#39;-1,2-Ethanediylbisoctadecanamide.</li>\r\n	<li>N,N&#39;-Ethylenedi(stearamide)</li>\r\n	<li>Ethylene distearylamide.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Ethylene Bis Stearamide manufacturers in India - Our Product</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Ethylene Bis Stearamide or EBS by MLA Group has low acid value ( free fatty acid ), high melting point, and excellent white colour, and high purity. Used as a high melting lubricant for engineering plastics, masterbatches, filler compounds, rubber, etc, EBS is compatible with most waxes and plasticizers. The polarity of its two central amide groups and the non-polarity of the two fatty chains make this product an excellent surface-active agent which is incompatible with virtually all solvents and most polymer systems. When incorporated into polymers it &ldquo;blooms&rdquo; to the surface, coating it with a monomolecular layer. Its incompatibility is the basis for several other properties and many of the product&#39;s commercial applications including its anti-static properties.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why choose us as your Ethylene Bis Stearamide suppliers and exporters in India?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our organization is customer-centric, based on improving product quality and protecting consumer interests, integrity and stability, focusing on win-win cooperation with partners, comprehensively establishing a market management system and product quality control system. We are a well-reputed name among exporters and suppliers of Ethylene Bis Stearamide in the world. Our flexible management mechanism, excellent product quality, standardized market operation, perfect service system, price advantage, professionalism, and after-sales service makes us stand out in the fierce market competition. We also have a fully equipped in-house plastic lab including a compound extrusion line and pelletizer, a PVC pipe extrusion line, Rheometer, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our Advantage</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>High-quality, authentic products</li>\r\n	<li>Timely response</li>\r\n	<li>Competitive market prices</li>\r\n	<li>Accurate, safe, and fast delivery</li>\r\n	<li>Technical back-up</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>FAQs</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>I&rsquo;m looking for Ethylene Bis Stearamide exporters in India. How do I know your products are genuine?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At MLA Group of Industries, we offer you authenticity and guarantee on all our products. As a leading Ethylene Bis Stearamide manufacturers in India, we make sure that all our products are in strict adherence to industry standards and policies. They pass through various inspections and quality tests before being dispatched. We have a 3-tier QC system including shopfloor, FQC, and CQC labs to ensure zero defect. Rest assured, you will never have a complaint regarding the quality or originality of our products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Why should I purchase Ethylene Bis Stearamide from MLA Group?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At MLA Group, we are committed to providing customer-oriented services. The tacit cooperation in product development, sales, and customer service, a deep understanding of the corporate tenet of &quot;creating value for customers&quot;, and the spirit of creating unlimited possibilities run through every detail of the company&#39;s operation and management. This is the reason why today we are one of the leading Ethylene Bis Stearamide suppliers in the world. Besides, we never overcharge our customers and there is no concept of opportunity cost in our company. Hence our prices are always most competitive both in domestic and international markets.</p>\r\n', '', '<h2>Applications</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Ethylene Bis Stearamide Uses</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Ethylene Bis Stearamide is an activator for various plastics and synthetic resins. It is a release agent, a pigment dispersant, a lubricant, a surface gloss agent, and an activator for rubber products, coating, Ink additives, etc. In India, we are a leading name among Ethylene Bis Stearamide suppliers.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Uses</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>As a lubricant</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>EBS has good internal and external lubricity, mold release and smoothness, can accelerate melting, reduce melt viscosity, save processing energy consumption, increase product toughness, extend mold life, and give products a good appearance. Mainly used for PVC.PE.PP.PS.ABS resin, but also for phenolic and amino plastics.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>As a general-purpose dispersant</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>EBS is used as a general-purpose dispersant for plastics and is widely used in PVC products. It can also be used in combination with other lubricants and has a very significant synergistic effect. In the rubber industry, it is used as an anti-blocking agent and release agent, as well as a hard rubber surface treatment agent.</p>\r\n', '2024-04-25 12:18:03', '2025-03-17 13:17:19');
