fficiency of our products at very reasonable prices. We never overcharge our customers and don&rsquo;t believe in the concept of opportunity cost.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>FAQs</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why should I choose MLA Group of industries as my Ethylene Glycol Distearate suppliers in India?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>At MLA Group, we manufacture EGDS using only genuine ingredients in order to ensure the highest quality of the product. Our company follows the most stringent parameters of purity, and precise chemical composition and stability, which brings out the efficacy of our products. All these qualities make us the best choice for you to choose us as your Ethylene Glycol Di Stearate suppliers and exporters in India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What kind of products and services can I expect if I choose MLA Group as my Ethylene Glycol Di Stearate manufacturers in India?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our company is solely guided by the trust of our clients. We have rightfully gained this trust over the years by providing only the highest quality products and ensuring that our products are packed tamper-proof, so as to retain their quality during transportation. We also provide technical support to clients to advise on the handling and application of raw materials, as well as revision and/or suggestions for modification of formulations according to the client&#39;s needs.</p>\r\n', '', '<h2>Applications of Ethylene Glycol Di Stearates (EGDS)</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our company has been one of the Leading Ethylene Glycol Di Stearate suppliers in India. We cater to several different industries with our high-quality products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some of the most common uses of EGDS are as under:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Used in personal care products and cosmetics, it acts as a pearlized agent, opacifier, thickener in creams, lotions, shampoos, and other personal cleansing formulations.</li>\r\n	<li>Used in body washes and hair care products, as pacifiers and lotions stabilizers for creams.</li>\r\n	<li>E