(81, 'Calcium Sulphate', 'calciumsulphate', 'Calcium Sulphate', 'Calcium Sulphate', 'test', 'product-image/calium.webp', '', '', 'Unpublished', '<h3>LIGHT CALCIUM SULPHATE</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This product is an amorphous calcium sulphate and unlike the natural and its processed forms (gypsum etc.), it is very fluffy, white, pure and fine. Hence the product is highly suitable for its calcium contents utilization and other properties in applications where chemical purity and physical properties are important.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n', NULL, '<h3>Applications</h3>\n<ul>\n	<li>&nbsp;Food Items</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;Pharmaceuticals</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;Dyes &amp; Pigments</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;Paints, Paper, Rubber as a filler</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;Plastics</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;Beer</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;Portland</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;Cosmetics</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;Ceramics</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;Chemicals</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;Fertilizers</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;Desiccant</li>\n</ul>\n', '2024-06-30 11:37:51', '2024-10-05 07:48:41'),
(82, 'PE Wax', 'pe-wax-manufacturers', 'Leading manufacturer & supplier of PE Wax in India', 'We are identified as one of the most prominent PE Wax manufacturers & suppliers, based in India. We are also leading bulk exporter of PE Wax in the world.', '	<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\r\n	{\r\n	  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\r\n	  \"@type\": \"FAQPage\",\r\n	  \"mainEntity\": [{\r\n		\"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n		\"name\": \"How to identify good quality PE Wax?\",\r\n		\"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n		  \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n		  \"text\": \"<p>There are many unrefined or semi-refined PE waxes in the market which have hardness 8-20. Our PE wax colour is brilliant white. When you touch it with your hands, the genuine product has good smoothness. It feels like plastic rather than wax. It is hard, brittle, fragile, and does not form a mass at room temperature. Paraffin-containing fakes are greasy, greasy to the touch, feel like touching candles, or rough, look like unreconciled dough pieces, soft and sticky. If you hold them with your hands, they will form a ball. The genuine product smells like plastic, while the fake product smells of paraffin wax or a strong peculiar smell. </p> \"\r\n		}\r\n	  },{\r\n		\"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n		\"name\": \"Why should I purchase PE Wax from MLA Group?  \",\r\n		\"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n		  \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n		  \"text\": \"<p>As a leading manufacturer and supplier of PE Wax, we only manufacture premium quality products at leading market prices. Our PE wax is brilliant white in color and generally has a viscosity below 100 cps, majorly below 50 cps, so its flow is high, which is beneficial for lubrication and is suitable for general masterbatche, PVC pipes, profiles, compounds and most other applications.</p> \"\r\n		}\r\n	  },{\r\n		\"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n		\"name\": \"Is UNILUB PE Wax equivalent to Clariant / Honeywell / BASF grades?\",\r\n		\"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n		  \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n		  \"text\": \"<p>Ours is a refined PE wax which is much cheaper than the above speciality waxes which are made by chemical polymerization and cost almost double. However our waxes replace some of their grades successfully, where melting point and viscosity requirement is not very different from our specifications. Oxidized PE waxes are also different from our product. </p>\"  \r\n		}\r\n	  }]\r\n	}\r\n	</script>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Leading manufacturer & supplier of PE Wax in India\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"We are identified as one of the most prominent PE Wax manufacturers & suppliers, based in India. We are also leading bulk exporter of PE Wax in the world.\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/pe-wax.webp \" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/pe-wax-manufacturers.html \" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:logo\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/images/logo-MLA.png\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/pe-wax-manufacturers.html \">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Leading manufacturer & supplier of PE Wax in India\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/pe-wax.webp\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"We are identified as one of the most prominent PE Wax manufacturers & suppliers, based in India. We are also leading bulk exporter of PE Wax in the world.\" />\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:creator\" content=\"MLA Group\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'product-image/pe-wax.webp', NULL, '21', 'Unpublished', '<h2>Leading PE Wax manufacturers in India</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group of Industries is a leading PE Wax manufacturers in India with 600 tons per month refinery for polyethylene Wax ( PE Wax ) in India. Our industrial-grade PE Wax is a versatile product that is used extensively in varied industries like the plastic industry, rubber industry, wax industry, road marking paints, and many more. Due to our large installed capacity and sourcing of raw material from petrochemical plants all over the world, our prices are very competitive. Also, our quality is the most consistent due to the short path distillation that we follow to separate the free oil and moisture fully from the raw material, yielding a high-quality product with crisp white flakes or granules which makes us one of the leading PE Wax suppliers in the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Product - PE Wax</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We are a trusted PE Wax exporter in India that supplies premium quality wax. PE Wax is a refined wax made from low polymer waxes from petrochemicals industries by refining and distillation to remove the water and solvents and low molecular chains. It melts on heating to around 100 deg c and provides external lubrication in products like PVC pipes and profiles, masterbatches, road marking paints, and many other applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>General Properties of MLA UNILUB PE Wax:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Low viscosity, high softening point, good toughness</li>\r\n	<li>Non-toxic, excellent thermostability, low volatility, and aids better pigment dispersion.</li>\r\n	<li>External lubricant and internal lubricant ( as per the formulation ) that can improve plastic processing production efficiency and appearance of finished products.</li>\r\n	<li>It can improve the strength of plastic products, promote the plasticization of PVC products, improve the lubricating effect, and increase the gloss of the surface.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Properties of good quality PE Waxes supplied by MLA Group:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A good PE wax should be crisp (non-oily) which is reflected in its penetration hardness.</li>\r\n	<li>A good PE wax for masterbatches or PVC with minimum oil content has hardness 4-6. As the hardness increases, it becomes more costly and is used in specialty applications and as it decreases it becomes more oily and sticky.</li>\r\n	<li>There are many unrefined or semi-refined PE waxes in the market which have hardness 8-20. Our PE wax colour is brilliant white.</li>\r\n	<li>As the average molecular chain length increases the wax becomes more viscous. Our wax generally has a viscosity below 50 cps, so its flow is high, which is beneficial for lubrication and is suitable for general masterbatches and PVC applications.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why Choose MLA Group as your PE Wax Suppliers ?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As a leading PE Wax exporter in India, and in the world, we have established long-term and stable business relationships with many reputable clients. We are committed to providing our customers with the best quality products at leading market rates. With fast and reliable supplies, we have grown into one of the most prominent UNILUB brand of PE Wax exporters in the World, and have won the trust of many customers in different industries.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Advantage:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Professional PE wax manufacturing and supplying based in India.</li>\r\n	<li>With 75 years of working with experienced engineers and manufacturing high-quality PE wax, we help our customers to optimize their production formula, reduce product cost, and improve product quality.</li>\r\n	<li>In house application labs for PVC extrusion and masterbatches</li>\r\n	<li>DSIR recognized in house R&amp;D equipped with laser particle size analyzer, BET surface area analyzer, rheometers, extruders etc</li>\r\n	<li>In house plastic laboratory equipped with a rheometer, VR testing, two rolls, etc</li>\r\n	<li>Three-tier quality control system.</li>\r\n	<li>Fast decision making due to the flat structure</li>\r\n	<li>With a professional and experienced service team, we will reply to you and attend you within 24 hours, whether you need a product quotation or technical problem solution</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>For Further Information Assistance In Relation To Product Details, Please Do Not Hesitate To Contact Us.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>FAQs</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">How to identify good quality PE Wax?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are many unrefined or semi-refined PE waxes in the market which have hardness 8-20. Our PE wax colour is brilliant white. When you touch it with your hands, the genuine product has good smoothness. It feels like plastic rather than wax. It is hard, brittle, fragile, and does not form a mass at room temperature. Paraffin-containing fakes are greasy, greasy to the touch, feel like touching candles, or rough, look like unreconciled dough pieces, soft and sticky. If you hold them with your hands, they will form a ball. The genuine product smells like plastic, while the fake product smells of paraffin wax or a strong peculiar smell.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">Why should I purchase PE Wax from MLA Group?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a leading manufacturer and supplier of PE Wax, we only manufacture premium quality products at leading market prices. Our PE wax is brilliant white in color and generally has a viscosity below 100 cps, majorly below 50 cps, so its flow is high, which is beneficial for lubrication and is suitable for general masterbatche, PVC pipes, profiles, compounds and most other applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">Is UNILUB PE Wax equivalent to Clariant / Honeywell / BASF grades?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ours is a refined PE wax which is much cheaper than the above speciality waxes which are made by chemical polymerization and cost almost double. However our waxes replace some of their grades successfully, where melting point and viscosity requirement is not very different from our specifications. Oxidized PE waxes are also different from our product.</p>\r\n', '', '<h2>Applications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As a leading PE Wax manufacturers in the World, we produce superior quality PE Wax that can be widely used in the manufacture of masterbatch, granulation, plastic, steel, PVC pipe, hot melt adhesive, rubber, shoe polish, leather brightener, cable insulation material, floor wax, plastic profile, ink, injection molding, and other products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Other uses Of PE Wax include:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;<strong>Lubricant:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Due to its excellent external lubrication effect and strong internal lubrication effect, it has good compatibility with polyethylene, polyvinyl chloride, polypropylene, and other resins, and can be used as a product in extrusion, calendering, and injection moulding.</li>\r\n	<li>It can be used as a lubricating dispersant for filler masterbatch and degradation masterbatch, it can improve the processing performance, surface gloss, lubricity, and thermal stability of HDPE, PP, and PVC.</li>\r\n	<li>It can also be used as a lubricant for cable insulation materials.</li>\r\n	<li>As an anti-slip agent, It can improve the gloss, durability, hardness, and abrasion resistance of paper, increase water resistance and chemical resistance, and increase the aesthetics of paper.</li>\r\n	<li>As a rubber processing aid, it can enhance the diffusion of fillers, increase the extrusion molding rate, increase mold flow, and facilitate demolding.</li>\r\n	<li>As a pigment carrier. It has good light resistance and chemical properties that can improve the abrasion resistance of paints and inks, improve the dispersion of pigments and fillers, prevent pigments from sinking, and can be used as a flattening agent for paints and inks</li>\r\n	<li>In addition, it can also be used to make shoe polish, candles, crayons, cosmetics, leather agents, hot melt adhesives, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2024-09-12 10:38:58', '2025-03-17 13:51:49'),
(83, 'Glycerol Monostearate (Gms)', 'glycerol-monostearate-manufacturers-in-india', 'Leading Glycerol Monostearate Manufacturers in India', 'MLA Group is a leading manufacturer & supplier of Glycerol Monostearate, we are one of the best exporters of GMS in the world offering the best price.', '<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Leading Glycerol Monostearate Manufacturers in India\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"MLA Group is a leading manufacturer & supplier of Glycerol Monostearate, we are one of the best exporters of GMS in the world offering the best price.\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/calcium-hydroxide-pharma-grade_1_2_3.webp\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/glycerol-monostearate-manufacturers-in-india.html\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:logo\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/images/logo-MLA.png\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/glycerol-monostearate-manufacturers-in-india.html\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Leading Glycerol Monostearate Manufacturers in India\r\n\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/calcium-hydroxide-pharma-grade_1_2_3.webp\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"MLA Group is a leading manufacturer & supplier of Glycerol Monostearate, we are one of the best exporters of GMS in the world offering the best price.\" />\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:creator\" content=\"MLA Group\">\r\n', 'product-image/calcium-hydroxide-pharma-grade_1_2_3.webp', NULL, '', 'Unpublished', '<h2>Glycerol Monostearate (Gms)</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group is one of the leading Glycerol Monostearate manufacturers in the world. Our brand is hailed as a symbol of quality and we are known as the most reliable Glycerol Monostearate exporter in India. Our stringent quality control and fast customer services make us the top Glycerol Monostearate suppliers in India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We exercise strict control at the raw material, semi-finished, and finished product stage to ensure the stability of the quality of the finished products (GMS in this case). The quality control is coordinated in a three-tier system-: the shopfloor lab, the factory quality control, and the central quality control.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Product - Glycerol Monostearate (Gms)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>UNILUB-GMS-40 is a refined glycerol monostearate made from triple pressed highest quality food grade stearic acid and CP grade glycerine. It is made under controlled conditions to ensure purity and suitability for polymer as well as food applications. It is available in self-emulsifying (SE) and nonself-emulsifying (NSE) grades, in powder/flakes form as required in the application.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why choose us as your Glycerol Monostearate supplier?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group, a Leading Glycerol Monostearate manufacturer in India, supplies premium quality Glycerol Monostearate that is widely used in several industries such as the pharmaceutical industry, plastics, polishes, cosmetics, shoe waxes, plastic lubricant, etc. GMS from the MLA group is available in both powder and flakes form and it is available in self-emulsifying ( SE ) and non-self-emulsifying ( NSE ) grades. SE grades are mostly used in bakery applications and NSE in chewing gums etc. In plastics SE or NSE both can be used. In cosmetics, SE grade is mostly used.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At MLA Group, we incorporate R&amp;D, production, and sales into one consistent delightful experience for our customers. Depending on new advances from our in-house R&amp;D and reliable product quality guarantee, backed with applied research and technical services, we have created a national high-tech enterprise that is among the top Glycerol Monostearate exporters in India. We have in-house application labs to check the performance of our product in rubber, plastics, and paints and have gone to the extent of installing high-speed mixers, two roll mills, molding, rheometer, extruders, and other pilot plants to check for the perfect performance of our product in these applications and continually improve the quality. We additionally utilize these labs for offering free specialized types of assistance to our customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All specifications given here are only indicative, there are several application specific grades under each category, please write to us for exact specifications.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Uses Of Glycerol Monostearate</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Use in Toffees</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>It is directly used in melted toffees by a weight of 0.2% of the dosage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The addition of GMS can help bind the oil and oil-based flavoring into a confection, reducing sweating and problems with rancidity. One property of emulsifiers that is particularly important is the improvement in emulsification in high-fat content confections such as butterscotch and caramels. During the manufacturing process, the high-sugar content syrup is produced in which fat globules are dispersed. The finer these globules are, the better will be the eating qualities. The higher the level of water left in a confection of this type, the higher the danger of stickiness and graining, GMS is a highly effective emulsifier to ensure maximum fat dispersion and minimum stickiness.</p>\r\n', '', '<h2>Applications</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Food Grade (40% monostearate)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This grade is manufactured using Food Grade Glycerine and Triple Pressed Cosmetic Grade Stearic Acid primarily for the food manufacturers, in particular for the Bread and Biscuit Manufacturers This Product has an off-white/cream colour and is also available in both SE (self-emulsifying) and NSE (Non-self-emulsifying) grade.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GMS is an essential component in the manufacturer of ice cream along with natural gums. It allows for a homogenous mix of water and fats and prevents the formation of icicles in the ice cream mixture.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also extensively used in:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Baked goods e.g. bread, cakes.</li>\r\n	<li>Confectionery e.g. chewing gums, toffees, caramels.</li>\r\n	<li>Dairy Products e.g. synthetic creams, desserts, ice cream.</li>\r\n	<li>Fats e.g. margarine, shortenings.</li>\r\n	<li>Starch e.g. mashed potatoes, pasta.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Industrial Grade</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This product contains 30% monoester and is not of Food Grade/Pharmaceutical Grade quality but is widely used by cost-conscious, low-quality manufacturers of Bread, Biscuits, and other food products as well as in PVC. It helps to increase the shine and flow in PVC pipes and other products being a very good multi-functional lubricant.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Non &ndash; Food Application</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cosmetic Creams</li>\r\n	<li>Pharmaceutical Preparations</li>\r\n	<li>Cement and Concrete additives</li>\r\n	<li>Polishes</li>\r\n	<li>Shoe Waxes</li>\r\n	<li>Plastic lubricant</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2024-09-27 13:53:15', '2025-03-31 11:23:07');
